"""
# Async TLS I/O (stub)

Placeholder for async TLS stream/listener. The full implementation
requires:
  - rt_byte_char(v: i64) -> text extern for correct wire encoding
  - rt_rsa_decrypt extern for ClientKeyExchange pre-master secret
  - AES-GCM bulk encryption externs for record-layer cipher
  - TLS 1.2 server state machine built on tuple-based primitives
    in nogc_sync_mut/tls/{handshake,record,cipher}.spl

The architecture is validated — see git history for the structural
